    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is judged credible for its intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index (RH < 1) acceptance criterion is met at all five operating conditions.",
